---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'top-picks', text: 'Top Picks', level: 2 },
  { id: 'why-apps-matter', text: 'Why Apps Matter', level: 2 },
  { id: 'comparison-table', text: 'App Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'detailed-reviews', text: 'Detailed Reviews', level: 2 },
  { id: 'key-features', text: 'Key App Features', level: 2 },
  { id: 'digital-tools', text: 'Digital Tools', level: 2 },
  { id: 'faqs', text: 'FAQs', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Claims Processing Insurance', href: '/best/claims-processing-insurance' },
  { title: 'Telemedicine Insurance', href: '/best/telemedicine-insurance' },
  { title: 'Digital Nomad Insurance', href: '/best/digital-nomad-insurance' },
  { title: 'Cigna Global Review', href: '/providers/cigna-global' },
  { title: 'SafetyWing Review', href: '/providers/safetywing' },
];

const comparisonColumns = [
  { key: 'provider', header: 'Provider' },
  { key: 'appQuality', header: 'App Quality' },
  { key: 'claimSubmit', header: 'Claim Submission' },
  { key: 'providerSearch', header: 'Provider Finder' },
  { key: 'digitalCard', header: 'Digital ID Card' },
];

const comparisonRows = [
  { provider: 'Cigna Global', appQuality: 'Excellent', claimSubmit: 'Photo submit', providerSearch: 'Yes', digitalCard: 'Yes' },
  { provider: 'SafetyWing', appQuality: 'Very Good', claimSubmit: 'In-app', providerSearch: 'Basic', digitalCard: 'Yes' },
  { provider: 'Bupa Global', appQuality: 'Good', claimSubmit: 'In-app', providerSearch: 'Yes', digitalCard: 'Yes' },
  { provider: 'Allianz Care', appQuality: 'Good', claimSubmit: 'In-app', providerSearch: 'Yes', digitalCard: 'Yes' },
  { provider: 'IMG Global', appQuality: 'Basic', claimSubmit: 'Portal', providerSearch: 'Limited', digitalCard: 'Yes' },
];

const featuresColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'App Feature' },
  { key: 'value', header: 'Why It Matters' },
  { key: 'availability', header: 'Who Has It' },
];

const featuresRows = [
  { feature: 'Photo claim submission', value: 'Submit claims instantly by photo', availability: 'Cigna, Bupa, Allianz' },
  { feature: 'Real-time claim tracking', value: 'Know status without calling', availability: 'Most major insurers' },
  { feature: 'Digital ID card', value: 'Never forget your card', availability: 'All major insurers' },
  { feature: 'Provider search', value: 'Find doctors and hospitals', availability: 'Most major insurers' },
  { feature: 'Telemedicine access', value: 'Video doctor visits', availability: 'Cigna, Bupa, SafetyWing' },
  { feature: 'Coverage lookup', value: 'Check what\'s covered', availability: 'Some insurers' },
  { feature: 'Pre-authorization', value: 'Request approval in-app', availability: 'Premium insurers' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Best Expat Insurance Mobile Apps 2026"
  description="Compare international health insurance by mobile app quality. Find insurers with the best apps for claims, provider search, telemedicine, and digital ID cards."
  headline="Best Expat Insurance Mobile Apps"
  subheadline="A good mobile app makes insurance easier—submit claims by photo, find doctors nearby, and access telemedicine. Here are the insurers with the best digital experience."
  heroImage="/images/answers/best-app-experience-insurance.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  showHeroCta={false}
  ctaButtonText="Compare Plans"
  ctaButtonHref="/compare/"
>
  <h2 id="top-picks">Top Picks for Mobile Apps</h2>
  <p>
    These insurers have the best mobile app experiences:
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">📱</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Mobile App</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-2">Cigna Global</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Industry-leading app with photo claim submission, provider search, and telemedicine access.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🎯</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best for Digital Nomads</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">SafetyWing</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Modern app built for remote workers with simple claims and digital-first experience.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🏥</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Provider Search</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">Cigna Global</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Excellent in-app provider search with filters for specialty, language, and direct billing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">💊</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Telemedicine Integration</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">Cigna Global</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Telemedicine built into the app—start video consultation with a few taps.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="why-apps-matter">Why Mobile Apps Matter</h2>
  <p>
    A good insurance app simplifies your life abroad:
  </p>

  <h3>Convenience When You Need It</h3>
  <p>
    Mobile apps provide instant access:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Submit claims while still at the doctor</li>
    <li>Find nearby hospitals in emergencies</li>
    <li>Access your ID card without physical wallet</li>
    <li>Check coverage before seeking care</li>
    <li>Start telemedicine visits anywhere</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Faster Claims Processing</h3>
  <p>
    App submissions are processed faster:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Photo upload is instant (no scanning, mailing)</li>
    <li>Digital submissions enter system immediately</li>
    <li>Missing information flagged right away</li>
    <li>Track status in real-time</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Better for Mobile Lifestyles</h3>
  <p>
    Expats and nomads benefit most:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Always have your insurance info with you</li>
    <li>Works across countries and time zones</li>
    <li>No need to find printers or mail services</li>
    <li>Manage insurance while traveling</li>
  </ul>

  <CTABox
    title="Go Digital"
    description="Compare insurers with the best mobile app experiences."
    buttonText="Compare Plans"
    buttonHref="/compare/"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="comparison-table">Mobile App Comparison</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={comparisonColumns} rows={comparisonRows} />
  </div>

  <h2 id="detailed-reviews">Detailed Reviews</h2>

  <h3>Cigna Global — Best Mobile App</h3>
  <p>
    Cigna Global has invested heavily in their digital experience.
  </p>
  <p><strong>What works well:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Excellent app design and usability</li>
    <li>Photo claim submission—snap and send</li>
    <li>Real-time claim status tracking</li>
    <li>Comprehensive provider search</li>
    <li>Filter by specialty, language, direct billing</li>
    <li>Telemedicine built into app</li>
    <li>Digital ID card always available</li>
    <li>Coverage information accessible</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Considerations:</strong> App quality matches premium pricing. Best-in-class digital experience. Worth it for those who value convenience.</p>
  <p><a href="/providers/cigna-global">Read our full Cigna Global review</a></p>

  <h3>SafetyWing — Best for Digital Nomads</h3>
  <p>
    SafetyWing built their product for the digital generation.
  </p>
  <p><strong>What works well:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Modern, clean app design</li>
    <li>Simple claim submission</li>
    <li>Digital-first approach</li>
    <li>Easy policy management</li>
    <li>Built for remote workers</li>
    <li>Telemedicine options</li>
    <li>No legacy system complexity</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Considerations:</strong> Less comprehensive than major insurers. Good for basic needs. Best for young, healthy nomads.</p>
  <p><a href="/providers/safetywing">Read our full SafetyWing review</a></p>

  <h3>Bupa Global — Good App with Premium Features</h3>
  <p>
    Bupa Global offers a solid app with premium plan features.
  </p>
  <p><strong>What works well:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Good app functionality</li>
    <li>Claim submission in-app</li>
    <li>Provider search available</li>
    <li>Digital ID card</li>
    <li>Telemedicine access</li>
    <li>Coverage information</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Considerations:</strong> App not quite as polished as Cigna. Still good experience. Matches their premium service reputation.</p>
  <p><a href="/providers/bupa-global">Read our full Bupa Global review</a></p>

  <h3>Allianz Care — Functional App</h3>
  <p>
    Allianz Care has a functional app covering essentials.
  </p>
  <p><strong>What works well:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Claim submission available</li>
    <li>Provider search</li>
    <li>Digital ID card</li>
    <li>Policy information access</li>
    <li>Multi-language support</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Considerations:</strong> Not as feature-rich as leaders. Gets the job done. Good enough for most needs.</p>
  <p><a href="/providers/allianz-care">Read our full Allianz Care review</a></p>

  <h2 id="key-features">Key App Features</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={featuresColumns} rows={featuresRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Photo Claim Submission</h3>
  <p>
    The most valuable app feature:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Take photo of receipt at doctor's office</li>
    <li>Add basic claim information</li>
    <li>Submit instantly</li>
    <li>No scanning, printing, or mailing</li>
    <li>Faster processing than other methods</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Provider Search</h3>
  <p>
    Find care when you need it:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Search by location (GPS or address)</li>
    <li>Filter by specialty</li>
    <li>Find English-speaking doctors</li>
    <li>Identify direct billing providers</li>
    <li>Get contact information and directions</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Digital ID Card</h3>
  <p>
    Always have your insurance info:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Display at hospitals and pharmacies</li>
    <li>Never forget or lose physical card</li>
    <li>All policy information accessible</li>
    <li>Emergency contact numbers included</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Telemedicine Access</h3>
  <p>
    Video doctor visits in-app:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Consult doctor from anywhere</li>
    <li>No need to find local providers</li>
    <li>Get prescriptions remotely</li>
    <li>Available 24/7 with some insurers</li>
    <li>Particularly valuable for travel and remote locations</li>
  </ul>

  <CTABox
    title="Modern Insurance Experience"
    description="Today's best insurers offer app-first digital experiences."
    buttonText="Compare Plans"
    buttonHref="/compare/"
  />

  <h2 id="digital-tools">Beyond Mobile Apps</h2>

  <h3>Online Member Portals</h3>
  <p>
    Web portals complement mobile apps:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Full account management</li>
    <li>Detailed claim history</li>
    <li>Download documents and forms</li>
    <li>Update personal information</li>
    <li>Better for complex tasks</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Digital Communication</h3>
  <p>
    Modern insurers offer multiple channels:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>In-app messaging</li>
    <li>Email communication</li>
    <li>Chat support</li>
    <li>Push notifications for claim updates</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Integration with Health Tools</h3>
  <p>
    Some apps connect to other services:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Health tracking integration</li>
    <li>Wellness program access</li>
    <li>Medical record storage</li>
    <li>Appointment scheduling</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="faqs">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

  <h3>Do all international insurers have mobile apps?</h3>
  <p>
    Most major insurers have apps, but quality varies significantly. Premium insurers (Cigna, Bupa) have better apps. Budget insurers may have basic apps or rely more on web portals. Check app store reviews before purchasing.
  </p>

  <h3>Can I submit all claims through the app?</h3>
  <p>
    Most routine claims can be submitted via app. Complex claims (hospitalization, large amounts) may require additional documentation through the portal. Photo submission works best for outpatient receipts and prescriptions.
  </p>

  <h3>Is the digital ID card accepted everywhere?</h3>
  <p>
    Generally yes at modern facilities. Some older hospitals may want a physical card. Best practice: have the app available but also carry your physical card as backup. Emergency information is accessible either way.
  </p>

  <h3>How does in-app telemedicine work?</h3>
  <p>
    Open the app, navigate to telemedicine, choose a doctor or get next available, and start video consultation. Some insurers use third-party telemedicine platforms accessible through the app. Prescriptions can be sent to local pharmacies.
  </p>

  <h3>Are insurance apps secure?</h3>
  <p>
    Major insurer apps use encryption and security measures to protect health information. Require password or biometric login. Still, be careful on public WiFi. Apps from established insurers are generally trustworthy.
  </p>

  <h3>What if I have issues with the app?</h3>
  <p>
    All insurers still offer phone and web portal options. App issues shouldn't prevent you from accessing care or filing claims. Customer support can help with app problems. Consider app as convenience, not sole access method.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This content is for informational purposes only. App features and quality change with updates. We are not insurance brokers. Always verify current app capabilities before purchasing a policy.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
